				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Mouse-Without-Borders.png?resize=558%2C180" alt="" title="Mouse-Without-Borders" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-105" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Mouse-Without-Borders.png?w=558&amp;ssl=1 558w, https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Mouse-Without-Borders.png?resize=300%2C96&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><br />
<a href="http://blogs.technet.com/b/next/archive/2011/09/09/microsoft-garage-download-mouse-without-borders.aspx" target="_blank">TechNet Blogs<br />
<img src="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/themes/colopixie/images/download.png" alt="download" class="sampleview" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></p>
<p>マウス・キーボード・ファイルのD＆DがLAN共有できるということで試してみました。</p>
<h3>インストール</h3>
<p>まずはマウスとキーボードを共有したいパソコンにインストールします。<br />
<a href="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0908.jpg" rel="lightbox[104]" title="DSC_0908"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0908-300x200.jpg?resize=300%2C200" alt="" title="DSC_0908" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-109" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0908.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0908.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><br />
進みます<br />
<a href="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0909.jpg" rel="lightbox[104]" title="DSC_0909"><img src="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0909-300x200.jpg?resize=300%2C200" alt="" title="DSC_0909" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-110" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0909.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0909.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><br />
進みます<br />
<a href="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0910.jpg" rel="lightbox[104]" title="DSC_0910"><img src="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0910-300x200.jpg?resize=300%2C200" alt="" title="DSC_0910" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-111" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0910.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0910.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><br />
この画面で”NO”を選択します。<br />
<a href="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0911.jpg" rel="lightbox[104]" title="DSC_0911"><img src="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0911-300x200.jpg?resize=300%2C200" alt="" title="DSC_0911" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-112" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0911.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0911.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><br />
そうするとセキュリティコードとPC名が表示されるのでそのままにしておくかメモります。</p>
<p>次に共有されたマウス・キーボードのほうでインストールします。<br />
<a href="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0912.jpg" rel="lightbox[104]" title="DSC_0912"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0912-300x200.jpg?resize=300%2C200" alt="" title="DSC_0912" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-113" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0912.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0912.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><br />
先程は”NO”を選択しましたが、今度は”YES”を選択します。<br />
<a href="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0913.jpg" rel="lightbox[104]" title="DSC_0913"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0913-300x200.jpg?resize=300%2C200" alt="" title="DSC_0913" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-114" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0913.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0913.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><br />
セキュリティコードとPC名を入力する画面がでてくるので先ほどのものを入力します。<br />
<a href="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0914.jpg" rel="lightbox[104]" title="DSC_0914"><img src="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0914-300x200.jpg?resize=300%2C200" alt="" title="DSC_0914" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-115" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0914.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0914.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><br />
NEXT</p>
<p><a href="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0915.jpg" rel="lightbox[104]" title="DSC_0915"><img src="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0915-300x200.jpg?resize=300%2C200" alt="" title="DSC_0915" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-116" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0915.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/DSC_0915.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><br />
画面の位置などを調整できます。</p>
<p>と、こんな感じでマウス・キーボード・ファイルの共有ができるてしまいます。<br />
インストール時にすこし重いかと思いましたが、インストール後はそれほど重くなく使えそうです。<br />
ただ、キーボード入力でJISとUSキーボードが混ざっている場合はキー配置がごっちゃになるのであまり使えないです。</p>
<p>一応動画もありますのでよかったらどうぞ。<br />
途中途中に説明をいれてあるはずです。</p>
